zones son iguales. En verdad, hemos aclarado los signos a gente que est\u00e1 convencida.","french":"118. Et ceux qui ne savent pas on dit : \"Pourquoi Allah ne nous parle-t-Il pas [directement], ou pourquoi un signe ne nous vient-il pas\" ? De m\u00eame, ceux d'avant eux disaient une parole semblable. Leurs coeurs se ressemblent. Nous avons clairement expos\u00e9 les signes pour des gens qui ont la foi ferme.","spell":"Waqaalal-ladziina laa ya'lamuuna laulaa yukallimunaallahu au ta'tiinaa aayatun kadzalika qaalal-ladziina min qablihim mitsla qaulihim tasyaabahat quluubuhum qad bai-yannaaaayaati liqaumin yuuqinuun(a)"},{"arabic":"\u0661\u0661\u0669.  \t\u0625\u0650\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0627 \u0623\u064e\u0631\u0652\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0652\u0646\u064e\u0627\u0643\u064e \u0628\u0650\u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0642\u0651\u0650 \u0628\u064e\u0634\u0650\u064a\u0631\u064b\u0627 \u0648\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0630\u0650\u064a\u0631\u064b\u0627 \u06d6 \u0648\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0627 \u062a\u064f\u0633\u0652\u0623\u064e\u0644\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0635\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062c\u064e\u062d\u0650\u064a\u0645\u0650","english":"119.  \tVerily, We have sent you (O Muhammad Peace be upon him ) with the truth (Isl\u00e2m), a bringer of glad tidings (for those who believe in what you brought, that they will enter Paradise) and a warner (for those who disbelieve in what you brought, they will enter the Hell-fire). And you will not be asked about the dwellers of the blazing Fire.","indonesian":"119. Sesungguhnya Kami telah mengutusmu (Muhammad) dengan kebenaran; sebagai pembawa berita gembira dan pemberi peringatan, dan kamu tidak akan diminta (pertanggungan jawab) tentang penghuni-penghuni neraka.","japanese":"119. &#26412;&#24403;&#12395;&#12431;&#12428;&#12399;&#65292;&#21513;&#22577;&#12392;&#35686;&#21578;&#12398;&#20253;&#36948;&#32773;&#12392;&#12375;&#12390;&#65292;&#12354;&#12394;&#12383;&#12434;&#30495;&#29702;&#12392;&#